{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/(main)/layout,_N_T_/(main)/learn/layout,_N_T_/(main)/learn/[type]/layout,_N_T_/(main)/learn/[type]/[level]/layout,_N_T_/(main)/learn/[type]/[level]/page,_N_T_/learn/foundation/beginner"},"segmentPaths":["/_tree","/_full","/!KG1haW4p/learn/$d$type/$d$level/__PAGE__","/!KG1haW4p/learn/$d$type/$d$level","/!KG1haW4p/learn/$d$type","/!KG1haW4p/learn","/!KG1haW4p","/_index","/_head"]},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/797e433ab948586e-s.p.0.q-h669a_dqa.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/caa3a2e1cccd8315-s.p.16t1db8_9y2o~.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/0.6dsdn7g3rv..css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/0j6kpnbwgrhei.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/14uv9l3-k2qh4.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/16sk4~vc8e6sh.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0c9ih0_ge37cg.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/turbopack-02v2juswviadt.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0pe7_.ico216u.js\" async=\"\"></script><meta name=\"next-size-adjust\" content=\"\"/><title>AI 启蒙课入门教程 - AI工具市场</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"学习 AI 启蒙课 的入门知识\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.0x3dzn~oxb6tn.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/03~yq9q893hmn.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"geist_a71539c9-module__T19VSG__variable geist_mono_8d43a2aa-module__8Li5zG__variable antialiased\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"min-h-screen bg-gray-50\"><header class=\"bg-white border-b border-gray-200 sticky top-0 z-50\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-3\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3 hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-linear-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-white text-sm\">⚡</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><span class=\"text-xl font-bold bg-linear-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent\">AI 工具市场</span></div></a><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"relative w-72\"><div class=\"relative\"><svg class=\"absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-4 h-4 text-gray-400\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z\"></path></svg><input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"全局搜索...\" class=\"w-full pl-9 pr-4 py-2 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all\" value=\"\"/></div></div><a class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gray-100 hover:bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center text-lg transition-colors group\" title=\"学院\" href=\"/learn\"><span class=\"group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\">🎓</span></a><a href=\"http://hsinky.cn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gray-100 hover:bg-purple-100 flex items-center justify-center text-lg transition-colors group\" title=\"个人博客\"><span class=\"group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\">📰</span></a></div></div></header><div class=\"flex\"><aside class=\"w-72 bg-white border-r border-gray-200 flex flex-col fixed left-0 top-14 h-[calc(100vh-56px)]\"><nav class=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-4\"><div class=\"space-y-1\"><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🏠</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">首页</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">概览与推荐</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/skill\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">✨</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Skill</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">可复用的能力模块</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/mcp\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🔌</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">MCP</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">外部工具与服务接入</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/agent\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🤖</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Agent</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">自主决策的AI助手</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/prompt\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">📝</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Prompt</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">高效沟通的模板</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/workflow\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🔄</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Workflow</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">多步骤任务编排</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/knowledge\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🗃️</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Knowledge</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">企业知识智能检索</div></div></a></div></nav><div class=\"shrink-0 p-4 border-t border-gray-100 bg-white\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400\"><div>版本 v1.0.0</div><div class=\"mt-1\">© 2026 AI Tools Center</div></div></div></aside><main class=\"flex-1 ml-72\"><div class=\"p-8\"><nav class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6\"><a class=\"hover:text-gray-700 transition-colors\" href=\"/learn\">学院</a><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg><a class=\"hover:text-gray-700 transition-colors\" href=\"/learn/path/beginner\">入门路径</a><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-gray-900 font-medium\">AI 启蒙课</span></nav><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-violet-600 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white mb-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\"><span class=\"text-4xl\"></span><div><h1 class=\"text-2xl font-bold\">AI 启蒙课</h1><p class=\"text-white/80\">从零开始，建立对 AI 的正确认知</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 text-white/80 text-sm\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg><span>预计 <!-- -->90分钟</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg><span>入门路径</span></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-4 mb-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm\"><span class=\"text-gray-500\">难度选择：</span><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-blue-600 text-white\" href=\"/learn/foundation/beginner\">入门路径</a><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-200\" href=\"/learn/foundation/developer\">开发者路径</a><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-200\" href=\"/learn/foundation/architect\">架构师路径</a></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-8\"><div class=\"prose prose-gray max-w-none\"><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-indigo-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">1</span>第一课：AI 是什么？打破认知误区</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"bg-indigo-50 border-l-4 border-indigo-500 p-4 rounded-r-lg\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">核心问题</h3><p class=\"text-gray-700\">当我们谈论 AI，我们到底在谈论什么？</p></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h4 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">首先，让我们澄清最常见的误解：</h4><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div class=\"bg-red-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2 text-red-700\">误解：AI 有意识</h5><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">很多人认为 AI 在&quot;思考&quot;、&quot;理解&quot;。实际上，AI 只是在<strong>计算概率</strong>。</p></div><div class=\"bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2 text-green-700\">真相：AI 是数学</h5><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">AI 的本质是<strong>统计模型</strong>，它通过海量数据学习语言规律，预测下一个字是什么。</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-bold mb-3\">通俗理解：AI 是一个超级学生</h4><p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-3\">想象一个读遍了互联网所有文本的学生：</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-gray-600\"><li>• 当你问它问题，它不是在&quot;思考&quot;，而是在<strong>记忆中搜索最相关的组合</strong></li><li>• 它能回答的问题，都是数据中见过的<strong>模式</strong></li><li>• 它的错误，是因为概率上拼凑出了看似合理但不正确的内容（幻觉）</li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-bold mb-2 text-blue-700\">为什么它可能&quot;说谎&quot;？</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-700\">AI 的目标不是说真话，而是<strong>生成看起来合理的文本</strong>。它会基于概率生成内容， 有时候概率最高的答案是错的，但AI并不知道。这就是&quot;幻觉&quot;现象。<br/><strong class=\"text-blue-800\">关键结论：</strong>永远要验证AI的事实性回答，尤其是在医疗、金融等敏感领域。</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-indigo-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">2</span>第二课：大语言模型如何&quot;思考&quot;？Transformer 原理</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"bg-indigo-50 border-l-4 border-indigo-500 p-4 rounded-r-lg\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">核心问题</h3><p class=\"text-gray-700\">AI 具体是怎么理解文本并生成回答的？</p></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h4 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">第一步：把文字变成数字 - Tokenization</h4><div class=\"bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-3\">计算机不能直接处理文字，必须转换成数字：</p><div class=\"bg-gray-800 text-green-400 p-3 rounded font-mono text-sm\"><p>&quot;苹果公司发布了新手机&quot;</p><p class=\"mt-2\">→ [12823, 4567, 2341, 8901, 5678, 3456]</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-gray-400\">// 每个数字对应一个 Token（词元）</p></div><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2\">每个 Token 大约是 0.75 个英文单词或 1.5 个汉字</p></div></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h4 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">第二步：理解句子中词与词的关系 - Self-Attention</h4><div class=\"bg-purple-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">Transformer 的核心创新</h5><p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-3\">在 Transformer 之前，模型按顺序处理文字。Transformer 的<strong>自注意力机制</strong>让模型能同时关注句子中的所有词，理解它们之间的关联。</p><div class=\"bg-white p-3 rounded border\"><p class=\"text-sm font-medium mb-2\">示例：理解&quot;苹果&quot;的歧义</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">&quot;她买了一个苹果&quot; → <span class=\"text-red-600\">水果</span></p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">&quot;苹果公司发布了新手机&quot; → <span class=\"text-blue-600\">科技公司</span></p></div><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2\">模型通过注意力权重判断：第一个句子中&quot;苹果&quot;与&quot;买&quot;、&quot;吃&quot;相关度高，所以是水果</p></div></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h4 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">第三步：从输入到输出 - 预测下一个 Token</h4><div class=\"bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><div class=\"space-y-2\"><p class=\"text-gray-700\"><strong>大语言模型的工作方式：</strong>给定前面的文字，预测下一个</p><div class=\"bg-white p-3 rounded border\"><p>输入：&quot;今天天气&quot;</p><p class=\"text-gray-500\">模型预测：很热(0.45)、不错(0.25)、很冷(0.20)、...</p></div><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2\">不断重复这个过程：输入 → 预测下一个字 → 添加到输入 → 再预测...</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-yellow-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-bold mb-2 text-yellow-800\">重要概念：预训练、微调、RLHF</h4><div class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"font-bold text-blue-600\">预训练</span><span>读海量文本，学习语言规律。像学生读所有能找到的书。</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"font-bold text-green-600\">微调</span><span>针对特定任务再训练。像读完基础书后，专攻某个领域。</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"font-bold text-purple-600\">RLHF</span><span>人类反馈强化学习。让人类评分教会模型什么是&quot;好回答&quot;。这是模型变得&quot;听话&quot;的关键。</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-indigo-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">3</span>第三课：掌握核心参数 - 控制输出的关键</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"bg-indigo-50 border-l-4 border-indigo-500 p-4 rounded-r-lg\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">核心问题</h3><p class=\"text-gray-700\">如何让 AI 输出你想要的结果？</p></div><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div><h4 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">🌡️ Temperature (温度)</h4><div class=\"bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg space-y-3\"><p class=\"text-gray-700\">控制输出的随机性和创造性。值越大，输出越多样；值越小，输出越确定。</p><div class=\"space-y-2\"><div class=\"white p-3 rounded border border-blue-200\"><p class=\"text-sm font-medium text-blue-700\">Temperature = 0 - 绝对确定</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">每次输出都相同。适合：代码、算术、格式转换</p></div><div class=\"white p-3 rounded border border-blue-200\"><p class=\"text-sm font-medium text-blue-700\">Temperature = 0.7 - 平衡</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">有一定创意但保持稳定。适合：写作、对话、分析</p></div><div class=\"white p-3 rounded border border-blue-200\"><p class=\"text-sm font-medium text-blue-700\">Temperature = 1.0+ - 高创意</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">输出随机且多样。适合：头脑风暴、创意生成</p></div></div></div></div><div><h4 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">📊 Top-P &amp; Top-K</h4><div class=\"bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg space-y-2\"><p class=\"text-gray-700\">限制模型从概率最高的候选词中选择，避免生成不合理的内容。</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm\"><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-green-700\">Top-K</p><p class=\"text-gray-600\">只保留最可能的 K 个词</p></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-green-700\">Top-P</p><p class=\"text-gray-600\">累积概率达到 P 时停止</p></div></div><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">示例：Top-K=5 意味着只从最可能的5个候选词中选择</p></div></div><div><h4 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">🔄 Max Tokens &amp; Context Window</h4><div class=\"bg-orange-50 p-4 rounded-lg space-y-2\"><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-orange-700\">Context Window (上下文窗口)</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">模型能处理的最大 Token 数量（包括输入 + 输出）。GPT-4 约 128K Token ≈ 10 万汉字。</p></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-orange-700\">Max Tokens</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">限制单次输出的最大长度。不设置可能浪费 Token 或触发截断。</p></div><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 bg-white p-2 rounded border\">实战建议：长文本需要分段处理，超出的内容会被截断</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-indigo-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">4</span>第四课：动手实践 - 你的第一个 AI 对话</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"bg-indigo-50 border-l-4 border-indigo-500 p-4 rounded-r-lg\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">实践任务</h3><p class=\"text-gray-700\">现在，让我们用 AI 完成一个实际任务</p></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h4 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">任务：让 AI 帮你分析一段新闻</h4><div class=\"bg-red-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2 text-red-700\">错误的问法</h5><div class=\"bg-gray-100 p-3 rounded font-mono text-sm\">&quot;帮我分析一下这个新闻&quot;</div><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2\">问题：太模糊，AI 不知道你想知道什么，可能会给出泛泛而谈的回答。</p></div><div class=\"bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2 text-green-700\">正确的问法</h5><div class=\"bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded font-mono text-sm whitespace-pre-wrap\">请分析以下新闻文章，提取以下信息并以 JSON 格式返回：\n\n## 新闻内容\n[在此粘贴你的新闻内容]\n\n## 要求\n1. 标题\n2. 主要事件（一句话总结）\n3. 关键人物\n4. 日期\n5. 地点\n6. 影响分析（正面/负面影响）\n\n## 输出格式\n{\n  &quot;title&quot;: &quot;新闻标题&quot;,\n  &quot;summary&quot;: &quot;一句话总结&quot;,\n  &quot;people&quot;: [&quot;人物1&quot;, &quot;人物2&quot;],\n  &quot;date&quot;: &quot;2024-03-07&quot;,\n  &quot;location&quot;: &quot;地点&quot;,\n  &quot;impact&quot;: {\n    &quot;type&quot;: &quot;正面/负面/中性&quot;,\n    &quot;analysis&quot;: &quot;影响分析&quot;\n  }\n}</div></div></div><div class=\"bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-bold mb-2 text-blue-700\">要点总结</h4><ul class=\"text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1\"><li>✅ 明确告诉 AI 你想要什么（提取信息）</li><li>✅ 提供具体的输出格式（JSON）</li><li>✅ 给出结构化的要求（列出需要的信息点）</li><li>✅ 避免模糊的表述（不用&quot;分析一下&quot;这种话）</li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-purple-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-bold mb-2 text-purple-700\">课后练习</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-700\">尝试用同样的方法，让 AI 帮你：1) 总结一份会议记录 2) 从邮件中提取关键信息 3) 分析用户反馈</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-8 flex items-center justify-between\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/learn/path/beginner\"><svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M15 19l-7-7 7-7\"></path></svg>返回<!-- -->入门路径</a><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/learn\">返回学院<svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main></div></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0j6kpnbwgrhei.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[30824,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"Providers\\\"]\\n3:I[87161,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n4:I[40715,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n5:I[78691,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pe7_.ico216u.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n6:I[30470,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pe7_.ico216u.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n8:I[98544,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"OutletBoundary\\\"]\\n9:\\\"$Sreact.suspense\\\"\\nc:I[98544,[\\\"/_next/